      Comparing Obama and Reagan After Tragedies 07/18/14


Friday, July 18, 2014



Today on The Glenn Beck Progam, 

   Glenn is joined by Dana Loesch to discuss WeWillNotConform.com.

   He is also joined by Barry Loudermilk to discuss his upcoming election
    for Congress in Georgia. 

   The guys also compare Barack Obama and Ronald Reagan's reaction to tragedy. 

          All this and more on The Glenn Beck Program!





The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET
